videos.description: Fans reported long delays getting into Mercedes-Benz Stadium for Georgia-Alabama game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Misc (Fans experience delay for CFP National Championship) 2018/01/08 Shortstop

videos.headline: Fans experience delay for CFP National Championship

videos.description: The Bulldogs and Crimson Tide are introduced and storm out of the tunnel.
videos.headline: Georgia and Alabama take the field

videos.description: Alabama's Tony Brown rips the ball away from  Javon Wims to intercept Jake Fromm on the opening possession of the College Football Playoff Championship.
videos.headline: Fromm throws INT on opening drive

videos.description: Crimson Tide quarterback Jalen Hurts follows his blockers for a 12-yard gain on the designed run.
videos.headline: Hurts rumbles for Alabama 1st down

videos.description: Alabama misses an opportunity to open the scoring when Andy Pappanastos botches a 40-yard field goal attempt.
videos.headline: Pappanastos' 40-yard FG attempt goes wide left

videos.description: The Bulldogs' defense holds strong on 3rd-and-3 and tackles Alabama quarterback Jalen Hurts behind the line of scrimmage.
videos.headline: Georgia defense stuffs Hurts on 3rd down

videos.description: The Bulldogs take a 3-0 lead after Rodrigo Blankenship drills a 41-yard field goal.
videos.headline: Georgia scores first with FG

videos.description: Jake Fromm finds Riley Ridley open over the middle for a 23-yard pickup on 3rd-and-8.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm hits Ridley for clutch 3rd-down conversion) 2018/1/8

videos.headline: Fromm hits Ridley for clutch 3rd-down conversion

videos.description: Georgia's Javon Wims makes the jumping catch and gets his hand down inbounds before he lands to complete the 16-yard gain.
videos.headline: Georgia's Wims gets arm inbounds on tough catch

videos.description: On 3rd-and-goal, Alabama brings the pressure and forces Jake Fromm to throw an incomplete pass over the middle. Georgia would make it 6-0 with a field goal.
videos.headline: Alabama holds Georgia to FG

videos.description: Jalen Hurts cuts through the Georgia defense on QB draw for a 31-yard pickup.
videos.headline: Hurts weaves through defense for 31 yards

videos.description: Bulldogs' quarterback Jake Fromm throws a 16-yard strike over the middle to Riley Ridley to convert on third down.
videos.headline: Riley Ridley moves chains for Georgia

videos.description: The Crimson Tide lose contain and Bulldogs' quarterback Jake Fromm scrambles and takes a hit after a 14-yard gain.
videos.headline: Fromm runs Georgia into red zone

videos.description: Georgia's Mecole Hardman takes a direct snap, sprints to the pylon for 1-yard TD run just before halftime.
videos.headline: Hardman runs in opening TD of CFP Championship

videos.description: Alabama trails Georgia 13-0 at half and head coach Nick Saban says that the offense's struggles do not all fall on quarterback Jalen Hurts.
videos.headline: Saban: 'We got to get open. We got to protect better'

videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart says that Alabama is "hard to move" up front, but Georgia's running backs are "running hard."
videos.headline: Smart sees 'composure, physicality'

videos.description: With Georgia's defense shutting down Alabama, Mecole Hardman's touchdown before the half has the Bulldogs up 13-0.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Georgia controlling momentum in 1st half) 2018/1/8 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Georgia controlling momentum in 1st half

videos.description: Mecole Hardman keeps it on the option and gets in from one yard out for the game's first touchdown to increase Georgia's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play Video (Georgia's TD provides energy boost before halftime) 2018/01/08 ENHL ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia's TD provides energy boost before halftime

videos.description: Sony Michel leads the way with 61 rushing yards in the 1st half as Georgia takes a 13-0 lead over Alabama in the CFP National Championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bulldogs' rungame stokes 13-0 lead at halftime) 2018/01/08 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Bulldogs' run game stokes 13-0 lead at halftime

videos.description: Sony Michel tightropes the sidelines with some nifty footwork for a 26-yard pickup.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michel creates magic tiptoeing on key run) 2018/1/8 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Michel creates magic tiptoeing on key run

videos.description: Alabama freshman QB Tua Tagovailoa starts the second half for the Crimson Tide and is sacked by Butkus Award winner Roquan Smith on third down.
videos.headline: Tagovailoa replaces Hurts to start 2nd half, goes 3-and-out

videos.description: Alabama QB Tua Tagovailoa breaks free of Georgia defenders, runs to the other side of the field for a 3rd-down conversion.
videos.headline: Tagovailoa shows amazing escapability on 1st-down run

videos.description: Alabama quarterback Tua Tagovailoa concludes the 7-play drive with a 6-yard touchdown pass to Henry Ruggs III, and Jalen Hurts hugs Tagovailoa to celebrate.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tagaovailoa caps electric drive with TD pass) 2018/1/8

videos.headline: Tagaovailoa caps electric drive with TD pass

videos.description: Jake Fromm throws a perfect pass to Mecole Hardman on an electrifying 80-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm drops dime to Hardman for 80-yard TD) 2019/1/8

videos.headline: Fromm drops dime to Hardman for 80-yard TD

videos.description: Alabama QB Tua Tagovailoa rolls left and forces a throw into coverage as Georgia's Deandre Baker comes down with the pick.
videos.headline: Georgia pressures Tagaovailoa, forces INT

videos.description: Jake Fromm's pass deflects off a lineman's helmet and into the hands of Raekwon Davis for an interception.
videos.headline: Fromm gives the ball back to Bama

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa leads Alabama on a 7-play drive that ends in the Crimson Tide's first touchdown of the CFP National Championship.

videos.headline: Tagovailoa leads Bama to 1st TD

videos.description: Following a kickoff, Alabama's Mekhi Brown punches a Georgia player, and then gets in a dispute on the sidelines and has to be calmed down on the bench.

videos.headline: Bama's Brown throws punch, gets in sideline dispute

videos.description: Mecole Hardman scores the longest touchdown in College Football Playoff history and extends the Bulldogs' lead against the Crimson Tide.

videos.headline: Hardman electrifies Georgia faithful with 80-yard TD

videos.headline: Smith stonewalls Scarbrough on third-and-short

videos.headline: Alabama's McDonald collapses on sideline

videos.description: Georgia's Trenton Thompson unloads a massive hit on Alabama WR Cam Sims on a first-down reception.
videos.headline: Thompson lays huge hit on Sims

videos.headline: Harris bounces run for big Alabama gain

videos.headline: Jeudy's nice grab puts Bama in scoring position

videos.headline: Tagovailoa fires strike to Ridley to tie game in 4th quarter

videos.description: Nick Saban ties Bear Bryant for most national titles by a head coach, boosting his case as the best coach in the sport's history.

videos.headline: Saban reaches royal status with sixth championship

videos.description: Nick Saban is all smiles after a huge overtime win for his 6th national title, 5th with the Crimson Tide.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Saban: 'This is the happiest I've ever been in my life') 2018/1/9

videos.headline: Saban: 'This is the happiest I've ever been in my life'

videos.description: Alabama freshman QB Tua Tagovailoa describes when he knew he was coming into the national title game and what it's like to win.
videos.headline: Tagovailoa: Winning championship means the world

videos.description: Jalen Hurts chimes in on Tua Tagovailoa taking the Crimson Tide to a 26-23 victory to win the national championship.
videos.headline: Hurts' message to Tagovailoa: 'Just play your game'

videos.headline: Saban, Alabama hoist National Championship trophy
